name: Christmas Tree T-Shirt
description:
Karsenbarg Clothing
Christmas Tree T-Shirt


This listing is for the 'Christmas Tree' T-Shirt shown in the images.

This design comes in a range of colours and sizes. 
These T-shirts make great birthday & Christmas gifts.

All T-Shirts are printed using the latest digital vinyl transfer techniques.
All Karsenbarg Clothing designs are original artwork and will be made available for both men & women.
 
Please also check out the other designs we have available.

We use good quality garments that are machine washable, use a warm setting and wash inside out with similar colours.
Tumble dry on low heat. As with all printed items we recommend ironing inside out.

Garment Specifics
150 gsm
100% ringspun cotton
Fashion fit
Shoulder to shoulder taping
Rib neckline
Tubular body
Twin needle sleeves and hem

Size/Chest
M - 38/40
L - 42/44
XL - 46/48

(Garment sizes are approximate and for guidance only) 

Postage and Packaging
All orders are sent via Royal Mail and will usually be delivered within 3-5 working days of cleared payment being received.
